Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:04.70,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1000,0}dakara ima ichibyou goto ni sekaisen wo koete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:09.75,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}kimi no sono egao mamoritai no sa
