Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:22.93,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}nomikomarete yuku kodoku no kansokusha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:14.82,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even the world's billions of heartbeats
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:21.74,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are nothing to you but a fleeting and insignificant question
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:26.79,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We may be trapped in the past or lament the future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:32.71,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But predetermination does not allow the slightest mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:38.97,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The infinite dreams and imagined futures before us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:44.76,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are naught but vain theories we may hold
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:50.81,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}Finitude is what the two clock hands show
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:55.57,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}As they point toward a cruel destiny and choice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:04.70,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1000,0}And now I cross the boundary between worlds each second
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:09.75,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because I want to protect that smile of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:16.67,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And a loop in time without sadness will once again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:22.93,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Engulf me, a lonely observer
