Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiver, my right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the contract we made, I order you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to wreathe yourself in black flame and grant my desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't heat up my kara-age!
