Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:28.67,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri, this is no longer a microwave. It's a time machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you join the lab, you'll be dealing with this all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go buy me a new microwave, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to photograph me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, no photos!
