Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can use the Phone Microwave's cell phone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to send a D-mail to any phone you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Daru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's continue our experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really a time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think the landlord will get mad at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mr. Braun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call my dad Mr. Braun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the boss? He's out on a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he'll be back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't, I couldn't screw around outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juicy Kara-age #1 would taste better...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's no Dr Pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're out, keep looking until you find some!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a Dr Pepperian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want some or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of mad scientist worries about not getting enough vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the Round Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot in here. Let's open a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the Organization discovers our secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delusion fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now move Operation Urd to stage 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and run experiments to make the D-mail
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During summer, you need barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some, too, Moeka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practical? What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... That's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you create a time paradox...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant, as a scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you interested in whether we can alter the past, using the D-Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what will we change?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what I want to accomplish with this operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Okarin... Mayushii is very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}If I had money, I could buy new parts for the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}and I could go to May Queen all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:22.63,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,610)}We should work toward world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:27.51,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,610)}Like give everyone in the world an Upa cushion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Okabe, that's really lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an experiment to see if we can change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the easiest way to tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But basically, you just want money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Celeb 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cele... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celeb 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear anything from a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,living in a hotel on her parent's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are all kinds of lottery tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Moeka go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... Can't take my eyes off you for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you didn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she supposed to be a valley girl LOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christina, keep a close eye on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she doesn't wander around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see the lab, Moeka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii is good at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it for Kurisu-chan, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Loto 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every Thursday, the winning numbers are announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send the numbers to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have any other ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which number do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, first prize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200,000,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200,000,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200,000,000 yen is a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First prize would draw too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Organization is chasing me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got cold feet, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's second prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23,000,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,700,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe's chicken, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx89}That's coming from someone worried about a time paradox, Cel-7?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.84,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the Upa cushion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're tired or feeling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you give it a hug, like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the fridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your first Lab Member mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, your first job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of what to write in the D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will make the me of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one week ago want to buy a Lotto-6 ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be 168 hours,so about 170 seconds would do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the time has come to open Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really never tire of it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you need to stop whining about it every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I'm having fun, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, our assistant sure is a tsundere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's a tsundere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Miss Makise, you know what a tsundere is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you definitely responded like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm starting up the microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you create a time paradox...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy Congroo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many minutes have I been standing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About thirty seconds, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just talking about an experiment to see if we could change the past with a D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ran over to Phone Microwave-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and started panting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii, can you say "panting" again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe... Are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lotto-6!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cel-7, did I win third prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Cel-7...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did an experiment to see if we could change the past with the D-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just talking about what we could
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do for the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii wants something that will bring about world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like giving everyone in the world an Upa cushion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.90,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ruka-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma-san, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,02, 12, 18...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako! Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... You gave me the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said to buy it since it might win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Okarin's psychic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ruka, did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I got one of the numbers wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, did you use the Phone Microwave to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, there's no Dr Pepper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They didn't have any.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you want me to do about it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sent the D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's no record of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(1,515)}The past has been changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They didn't remember the experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though we all talked about it, and we all observed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This feeling! It's just like back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've been brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brainwashed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But was I the one brainwashed... Or were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's brainwashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hououin Kyouma, will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Nae's scared of Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}You mean when there are all those sparks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}You did it before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}There should have been one ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I didn't notice that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}What about you, Nae?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}You really are a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I'm not a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pervert gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know it was this bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear about the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nice job, I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me warn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about something related to the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not ask John Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, John Titor mentioned this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you go to the past and change it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this alters something called the divergence number,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the world line moves to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When there's a world line move, \Npeople's memories are altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And memories of the new world are created.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The D-mail moved the world line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from a world where Rukako didn't buy the Lotto-6 ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to one where he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world line changed, and so did the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't send the D-mailwith the winning Loto 6 number
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not that the other Lab Members don't remember the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why do I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nae, whatever he asks, don't tell him I was slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give me a ride on your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing with my daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I wasn't doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy like you couldn't control himself if left alone with my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always think about me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we weren't alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that true, Nae?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised, so I can't say she was slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Part-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 42-inch was left on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk about the reason why later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're stopping the experiment for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1020)}Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, assistant, you're not going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be all alone if you went back to the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you want me to spend time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, little Cel-7?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Cel-7!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta send this text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stay here, be quiet, The Zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the name that bugs me most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a girl, waiting for a message from her crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really want attention that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that message to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, I realized I made a huge mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mistake? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left my wallet at the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now I can't get into May Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru's with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to lend him money, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}And so, Okarin, do you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}If you don't, you can hug Mayushii's Upa, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Then you'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Good luck at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, you're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you suspected,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the past was changed, and the world line moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is why you retain your memories from before the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something similar happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The concept of changing the past
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,via e-mail was something that was never
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,envisaged, even in the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed the past and moved world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's never been confirmed that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone exists who can maintain their memories
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over a world-line jump, to observe the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma, you may have that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to lead the world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond Divergence 1%...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What lies beyond Divergence 1%?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What lies beyond it is true freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't cross that barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the future will become a dystopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you may be the one who has that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me change the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you to be the messiah.
